if pad_typ_int = PAD_TYPE_U_SHAPE then

gosub 1000
del 1 endif
add padwdt-0.03, 0, -padh a=a-2*padwdt+0.06 b=b-padwdt+0.03
next i
del pad_num

if not(et) then pdmod=ws_thk else pdmod=0 endif
add ws_thk, ws_thkin, pad_num*padh-padthk
for i=1 to pad_num
for j=0 to rnum-1 if iEntrance = ENTRANCE_SIDE and et = 0 then if entranceAxis > 1.5*entrance_width then cutpoly 4, 0, entranceAxis-entrance_width/2-ws_thk, 0, entranceAxis+entrance_width/2-ws_thk, pad_num*padh-padthk, entranceAxis+entrance_width/2-ws_thk, pad_num*padh-padthk, entranceAxis-entrance_width/2-ws_thk else cutpoly 4, 0, 0, 0, entranceAxis+entrance_width/2-ws_thk, pad_num*padh-padthk, entranceAxis+entrance_width/2-ws_thk, pad_num*padh-padthk, 0 endif prism_ 5, padthk, j*dr, 0, 15, j*dr, b-ws_thk-ws_thkin-j*dr, 15, j*dr+rsz, b-ws_thk-ws_thkin-j*dr-rsz, 15, j*dr+rsz, 0, 15, j*dr, 0, -1 cutend else prism_ 5, padthk, j*dr, et_melys*et+ws_thk, 15, j*dr, b-ws_thkin-ws_thk-j*dr, 15, j*dr+rsz, b-ws_thkin-ws_thk-j*dr-rsz, 15, j*dr+rsz, et_melys*et+ws_thk, 15, j*dr, et_melys*et+ws_thk, -1 endif

else
